title: Compiler panic - assertion failed: !self.has_escaping_regions()

labels.name: I-ICE
labels.description: Issue: The compiler panicked, giving an Internal Compilation Error (ICE) ❄️

body: Compiler panic. Found an ealier issue in the same file that had been closed because the problem had gone away in later compiles. This is the stable 1.1 though.
